                " angle of about 45-degree by means of a scintillation",
                " telescope."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Fissile targets were made from separated isotopes of",
                "tungsten in the WO(3) chemical form by means of",
                "vacuum evaporated onto aluminum backings.",
                "The thickness of the deposited layers about 2-mg/cm**2,",
                "have been defined by direct weighting and by Rutherford",
                "backscattering alpha-particles."
              ]
            }
